Pre-G Rank
    
    Queen Seltas:     Hall 3* "Royal Guard"
    Zamtrios:         Hall 3* "Advanced: Sand Sailor"
    Brute Tigrex:     Hall 6* "Ear Ache"
    Stygian Zinogre:  Hall 6* "Infernal Overlord"
    Deviljho:         Hall 7* "Devil of a Problem"
    Azure & Pink:     Hall 7* "Advanced: Speartip Menace"
    Gravios x2:       Hall 7* "Advanced: Speartip Menace"
    Daimyo Hermitaur: Village 7* "Skiff Scuttler"

G Rank

    Zamtrios x2: Hall 8* Grand Finals Confrontation
    Tidal Najarala is unlocked by gathering hall 8* Serpent Serenade
    Shrouded Nerscylla is unlocked by gathering hall 9* Cource Correction
    Diablos and Black Diablos is unlocked by gathering hall 9* Showdown at Midnight
    Deviljho and triple Tigrex I'm not as sure on, it's either when you clear your first 10* Apex fight or clearing all of the 10* Apex fights.







